                        <h3>Time Deposit Accounts</h3>
                        <p>Our Time Deposit Account is a fixed-term savings product that offers higher interest
                            rates compared to regular savings accounts. To open the account, a minimum initial
                            deposit of ₱5,000 is required.</p>
                        <p>Interest rates for time deposits are more competitive than those for regular savings
                            accounts and vary depending on the term length, with a minimum term of 30 days. You
                            can choose to receive interest payments either monthly or at the end of the term, based
                            on your financial needs.
                        </p>
                        <p>Just like our Power Build-up Savings Account, deposits in the Time Deposit Account are
                            insured by the Philippine Deposit Insurance Corporation (PDIC) for up to ₱500,000 per
                            depositor, giving you peace of mind while you grow your savings.
                        </p>
                        <p>Learn more about our Time Deposit Account <a href="<?php echo get_home_url(); ?>/mymoney/peso-time-deposit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>!</p>
